Q: Based on this review, would the user recommend this product? === Review: This product, a digital optical splitter, works great. I plugged in a digital audio cable from my DVD player into the splitter and now have both component video and audio from that source. The video is split so I can take one component cable with the video component to each TV. I have also split the audio into a component connector to a receiver so I can hear both TVs on the same speakers. I also have an RF connection hooked up to the splitter so I can change channels on the first TV and the video goes automatically to the second TV. I bought two of these splitters to be able to switch between these two sources when I am watching both TVs. The splitter is very good quality for a cheap price and it is just what I wanted for my system. Answer:

OPTIONS:
[+] No;
[+] Yes;
A: Yes

